OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780747879
OL,3,CTechnical issue detected on UK's
OL,4,Clargest warship HMS Prince of Wales
OL,6,FA technical issue has been detected on
OL,7,Fthe UK's largest warship as it was
OL,8,Fdocked at a port in Norway, the
OL,9,FMinistry of Defence (MoD) said.
OL,11,FEarlier this month, HMS Prince of
OL,12,FWales set sail from Loch Long, Argyll
OL,13,Fand Bute, Scotland, for Nordic waters
OL,14,Fto provide security in the Atlantic
OL,15,Fand High North regions.
OL,17,F"A minor technical issue" was
OL,18,Fidentified on the Royal Navy's most
OL,19,Fpowerful vessel during its latest stop
OL,20,Fin Stavanger, a port city in south-
OL,21,Fwestern Norway, the MoD said.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@YO]
