OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780747879
OL,3,CTechnical issue detected on UK's
OL,4,Clargest warship HMS Prince of Wales
OL,6,FThe aircraft carrier is expected to
OL,7,Fsail in the coming days, the ministry
OL,8,Fadded.
OL,10,FAn MoD spokesperson said: "HMS Prince
OL,11,Fof Wales is currently conducting a
OL,12,Fport visit to Stavanger as part of the
OL,13,FCarrier Strike Group's deployment
OL,14,Facross the North Atlantic and Arctic,
OL,15,Fwe expect her to set sail in the
OL,16,Fcoming days."
OL,26,@rD@[OUxD@MO]
