OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780747879
OL,3,CTechnical issue detected on UK's
OL,4,Clargest warship HMS Prince of Wales
OL,6,FThe ship, which is generally based in
OL,7,FPortsmouth, was joined by Type 45
OL,8,Fdestroyer HMS Duncan and tanker RFA
OL,9,F(Royal Fleet Auxiliary) Tidespring on
OL,10,Fits way to Nordic waters.
OL,12,FIt has worked with Nato and the Joint
OL,13,FExpeditionary Force throughout the
OL,14,Fdeployment.
OL,16,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
