OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780747879
OL,3,CTechnical issue detected on UK's
OL,4,Clargest warship HMS Prince of Wales
OL,6,FHMS Prince of Wales and HMS Queen
OL,7,FElizabeth are the largest and most
OL,8,Fpowerful vessels ever constructed for
OL,9,Fthe Royal Navy.
OL,11,FHMS Prince of Wales weighs 65,000
OL,12,Ftonnes, and has a top speed in excess
OL,13,Fof 25 knots per hour and a range of
OL,14,F10,000 nautical miles.
OL,16,FIt can carry up to 72 aircraft,
OL,17,Fincluding a maximum of 36 F-35B
OL,18,Ffighter jets, and has an expected
OL,19,Fservice life of up to 50 years,
OL,20,Faccording to the Royal Navy.
